<div class="main-col">
  <h2 class="content-heading">Designia Features</h2>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Animated Page Loading</h3>
  <p>Every page is loading with a nice smooth fade and slide animation. Try these links for content with a different size: <a href="index.php?content=home" class="ajax">Home</a>, <a href="index.php?content=services" class="ajax">Services</a>, <a href="index.php?content=contacts" class="ajax">Contacts</a></p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Popup Engine</h3>
  <p><strong>Designia</strong> has its own popup engine which allows you to call customizable popup windows with any HTML content or images inside.</p>
  <p>Popup windows with a different size and HTML content inside: <a href="?content=popup1" class="popup" rel="1000">width popup window</a>, <a href="?content=popup1" class="popup" rel="300">narrow popup window</a>, <a href="?content=popup1" class="popup" >default popup window</a>.</p>
  <p>Animated popup windows with images inside:</p>
  <p align="center"><a class="pop-image blink" href="images/1.jpg" rel="800"><img src="images/1s.jpg" width="150" height="107" alt="" /></a> <a class="pop-image  blink" href="images/2.jpg" rel="306"><img src="images/2s.jpg" width="57" height="107" alt="" /></a></p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Animated Menu with a TypeWriter effect</h3>
  <p><strong>Designia</strong> has the animated menu with nice hover effect and typewriter effect to display the link description.</p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Ajax Contact Form with validation</h3>
  <p><strong>Designia</strong> comes with Ajax Contact form with validation. It is available on the <a href="index.php?content=contacts" class="ajax">contacts</a> page or it could be opened through the <a href="index.php?content=contacts" class="popup">popup window</a>.</p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Search Engines Friendly Ajax</h3>
  <p><strong>Designia</strong> is powered with the Search Engines Friendly Ajax Engine. It is realized by means of PHP and Javascript. So be sure that the Search Engines will index all your ajax content correct.</p>
  <p>All "ajaxed" or "popup" links will be opened like these ones for search engines or visitors with disabled JavaScripts:<br />
    <a href="index.php?content=contacts">Contacts</a> | <a href="index.php?content=services">Services</a> </p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">Animated Portfolio Section</h3>
  <p>Designia has the great-looking slidable <a href="#" class="openFolio"><strong>portfolio section</strong></a> with a popup folio items.</p>
  <h3 class="inner-heading">and more:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Powered with jQuery</li>
    <li>100% tableless CSS</li>
    <li>Validates with XHTML 1.0 Transitional</li>
    <li>Easy to redesign, has very simple and clear API</li>
  </ul>
</div>
